{"tid":1171853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民唔明　引渡修例　樓市仆街　係開心　唔係驚嚇","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T08:05:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":8,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a7fca35ec4524299ad6bb173dd093d1e345f574d","tid":1171853,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/photos/a.282059205223293/2206899309405930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenryporterbabel%2Fphotos%2Fa.282059205223293%2F2206899309405930%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=e2c03854\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/photos/a.282059205223293/2206899309405930/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：無神論者的巴別塔<br />\n<br />\n所以我成日都話，離地黃屍點解永遠都唔會明白焦土論，係因為佢地根本唔係同社會嘅大多數人生活響同一層次<br />\n<br />\n對肥佬黎同何俊仁黎講，樓市仆街等於佢地仆街，但對好多香港中下階層黎講，樓市仆街卻係一種解脫<br />\n<br />\n你班黃屍成日以為恐嚇緊人，其實被恐嚇嘅就只有你地自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k952i9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk952i9F.png&h=d734ce55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFat Fat Wong:<br />\n聽到呢啲曲線撑惡法嘅蝦碌，好笑亦可悲<br />\n<br />\nStephen Wong:<br />\n想推銷一樣嘢而獲得最大效益一定係講一啲最多人都會中嘅 point，例如因為外國公司走會令失業率攀升，中小企會更難做生意，香港無啖好食等等<br />\n<br />\n無神論者的巴別塔:<br />\n呢班撚樣就算走都唔撚會賣樓，繼續響香港做業主剝削你班窮撚<br />\n<br />\nChiChung Choi:<br />\n前年計，差唔多可以上車，點知又升左；上年計又差唔多，再升；今年唔諗喇...咦，通過呢啲乜乜物物會大跌？<br />\n<br />\n我一定支持！<br />\n<br />\nRyan Pkyg Shiu:<br />\n渣住幾層樓係手點會同你焦土 佢地會焦埋"},{"pid":"8a5d6b9101b86841ede67ef0c3deddbac79c0247","tid":1171853,"uid":244332,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"外資走哂，轉哂中資咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1837dc55c4bdfd1f6e2d9de9cf60b53bfd7e4bd","tid":1171853,"uid":1